    {
        "content": "<p>as of july 2: \"It's a milestone day for Gophers and WebAssembly: the <code>wasi-preview-2</code> feature branch of TinyGo has landed in TinyGo's <code>dev</code> branch, bringing WASI P2 support to TinyGo!\"</p>",
